data.name: FLUID DRESS
data.c_fit: Fit: Tight — A close fit that hugs the body
data.c_seoProductDesc: Fit-and-flare cotton midi dress with Contour bodice
data.c_tabDescription: This is a strapless fit-and-flare dress. The bodice is cut from Aritzia's Contour — luxe, ultra-flattering fabric coveted for its smoothing effect and second-skin feel. The skirt is cut from airy, 100% cotton poplin with a smooth, crisp feel.
data.c_tabDetails:
• Content: 94% polyamide, 6% elastane; Lower Body: 100% cotton; Upper Body Lining: 94% polyamide, 6% elastane
  • Care: Machine wash
  • Imported
c_tabSizeFit: Length: Midi — Intended to hit between knee and low calf
